185
00:10:56,523 --> 00:11:00,790
<i>Paraneoplastic syndrome causes the body's
own antibodies to get thrown off track.</i>

186
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:03,728
They end up attacking the
brain instead of the tumor.

187
00:11:03,796 --> 00:11:06,493
